1
00:00:09,359 --> 00:00:11,320
Now eating these scraps we picked up

2
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,720
What kind of life is this?

3
00:00:12,919 --> 00:00:14,039
If you can't take it, turn yourself in

4
00:00:14,039 --> 00:00:14,960
Prison food's cleaner

5
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:24,600
Hey

6
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,679
Did you find Xiaoyu?

7
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:29,120
Whether he lives or dies, it's fate

8
00:00:29,519 --> 00:00:30,359
Just let him be

9
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,479
Boss Hui

10
00:00:32,799 --> 00:00:34,240
Being away from home so long

11
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,479
Do you regret it?

12
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:39,039
People like us

13
00:00:39,439 --> 00:00:40,280
can't have a family

14
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,399
A family's just a burden

15
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,320
Boss Hui, you're absolutely right

16
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:45,359
A man, you know

17
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:47,000
should put his career first

18
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,200
Our goal now is revenge

19
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:09,760
You're awake

20
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,000
Qibao

21
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,359
You finally see how good I am

22
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,519
I'm so thirsty

23
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,519
Guess I was flattering myself again

24
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:29,200
Hold on, I'll get you some water

25
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,760
I was so scared something happened to you

26
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,079
You have to stay safe

27
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,079
Okay?

28
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,280
Okay

29
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:42,760
I'll do as you say

30
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,959
Once you're feeling better

31
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,159
we'll start

32
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,719
a small business together

33
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,439
Live a peaceful life

34
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,480
From now on

35
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,319
I'll stay with you forever

36
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,719
He Siqi, time for your medicine

37
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:30,120
He Siqi, you must take your meds on time

38
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,400
What a beautiful day today

39
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:01,960
Right?

40
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,599
Don't be afraid

41
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:09,919
It's okay

42
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:12,479
Here

43
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,759
Have a piece of candy

44
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:19,000
You'll feel a lot better

45
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,840
I'm pretty much useless now

46
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:30,080
Why are you still so good to me?

47
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,240
Does being kind to someone

48
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,520
need a reason?

49
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,120
Anyway, when I'm good to you

50
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,639
it makes me happy too

51
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,680
That's enough for me

52
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,199
In this world

53
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,560
can you really get love

54
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,919
without paying any price?

55
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,039
Love that requires a price

56
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,520
just to be obtained

57
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,919
isn't real love, is it?

58
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:51,479
Think about it

59
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,439
Do you need conditions

60
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,400
to love yourself?

61
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:56,639
Anyway, as for me

62
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,879
I don't waste energy on stuff like this

63
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:01,000
I look at myself and like everything I see

64
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:03,520
And I feel the same about you

65
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,400
Even if no one loves me,

66
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,120
I'll still live my life well

67
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,319
and learn to love myself.

68
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,919
Oh, my dear

69
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,240
That's the right way to think

70
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,560
You know

71
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,199
self-love should be unapologetic

72
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:22,319
and happiness shouldn't need a reason

73
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,399
Right?

74
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:25,639
Here

75
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,360
Is it sweet?

76
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,399
Yes, it's sweet.

77
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:38,839
Let's go.

78
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,480
Slow down.

79
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,079
Let's take a walk on that bridge.

80
00:04:48,759 --> 00:04:50,240
Isn't that Chu Feng's car?

81
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:55,439
You're here.

82
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,279
We knew Siqi was being discharged today.

83
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,279
We came specially to pick her up.

84
00:04:59,279 --> 00:04:59,839
Didn't expect

85
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,000
you punk to beat us to it.

86
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:04,600
I'm with our Qibao 24/7.

87
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,480
You two

88
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,199
obviously can't compete.

89
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,399
Enough talk, hand me the stuff.

90
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,160
Get in the car.

91
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,720
Qibao, wait for me in the car.

92
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:15,839
Tianfang.

93
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:18,279
Ma Xiaojun's whereabouts are still unknown.

94
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,600
You and Siqi,

95
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,920
if you sense any danger, remember,

96
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,319
contact me immediately.

97
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:23,399
Don't try to be a hero.

98
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:25,240
I knew those two bastards

99
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,480
were up to no good.

100
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,279
If they dare mess with me again,

101
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,720
my fists won't go easy on them.

102
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,920
Save the tough talk.

103
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,959
Think hard

104
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:36,079
about how to build a good life with Siqi.

105
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:38,399
She needs company in her current state.

106
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,439
I'll move in with her first.

107
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,439
Once she gets better,

108
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,720
I'll go out, work, and make money.

109
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:44,319
Now that sounds like a real man.

110
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,600
Let me tell you,

111
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,759
within three months,

112
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:49,199
I'm opening 50 chain stores.

113
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,240
For me,

114
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,319
becoming rich is just around the corner.

115
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,120
I plan to raise capital first,

116
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:54,759
and then

117
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:56,639
make it onto the Forbes list.

118
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,160
And that's it.

119
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,879
Back in the day,

120
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:09,279
Old Master Sun, Qingyuan Manor's first head chef,

121
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,720
saw that I was clever and sharp,

122
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,519
dashing and charming,

123
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,720
a man with great potential.

124
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,639
So he wanted to take me as his apprentice,

125
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:17,680
and pass all his culinary skills on to me.

126
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:18,480
But alas,

127
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,680
back then,

128
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,319
my ambition wasn't in the kitchen.

129
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,120
So when he retired,

130
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:25,839
he gave me this shop and this prized cleaver.

131
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,399
He said one day,

132
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,279
should I ever fall on hard times,

133
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,519
I could rely on these

134
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:32,040
to make a comeback.

135
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:36,639
You're going to sell pork?

136
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,920
I'm about to

137
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:38,959
launch

138
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:41,040
a new era of pork-selling!

139
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,480
Wow, this scale is really heavy.

140
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,279
A dignified manor manager like me,

141
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:48,040
the head of a restaurant,

142
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,079
stooping down to sell pork,

143
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,920
and yet no one's coming by!

144
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,560
They've got no taste at all.

145
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,920
Coming! The scale's here!

146
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:56,800
Qibao,

147
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,680
how can I let you do such heavy work?

148
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,639
I like working.

149
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:01,920
When my body's tired,

150
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,319
my mind feels much lighter.

151
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,040
Alright then.

152
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,639
From now on,

153
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:06,839
you handle the money,

154
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:07,759
and I'll cut the meat.

155
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,959
You actually know how to do that?

156
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,240
Speaking of which,

157
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,439
I've got to tell you something.

158
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:14,079
Back in the day,

159
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,600
I learned from Chef Sun himself,

160
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,519
picked up some serious knife skills.

161
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,480
Cutting pork?

162
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:20,399
Piece of cake!

163
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,720
Really?

164
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,560
Watch closely.

165
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,360
Don't ruin the meat, or else...

166
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,120
How's that?

167
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,680
I thought you were bragging,

168
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,439
but you actually can do it!

169
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,759
You see,

170
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:33,959
I am

171
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,839
like a star in the dark night,

172
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:39,399
shining and captivating.

173
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:41,199
And what's more,

174
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,079
one of a kind!

175
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:46,279
So many people are watching.

176
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,759
Then let's discuss it in private.

177
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,639
Rat.

178
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,519
Hedgehog.

179
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,800
Where is the meat seller?

180
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,720
No, no, no,

181
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,399
we don't sell meat here.

182
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,199
Go buy it elsewhere.

183
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,199
Sir,

184
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,160
what kind of meat would you like?

185
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,560
Fox.

186
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,519
What fox?

187
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,680
I sell meat.

188
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:20,680
No, no, no,

189
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,680
we sell pork.

190
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:24,439
Give me

191
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:27,720
two pounds of Wu Song's cooked beef,

192
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,040
and also

193
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,279
the Chancellor's

194
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,399
pot of plum wine,

195
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:34,240
and one more,

196
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,960
a ginseng fruit,

197
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:38,759
to quench my thirst.

198
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:40,840
We don't have any.

199
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,200
Then this humble fellow

200
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,360
shall take his leave.

201
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,600
Look at you, everyone's gone.

202
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,120
How are you going to support me?

203
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:53,399
With my strong, sturdy chest, of course,

204
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:55,000
and this handsome face,

205
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:57,440
and a heart that loves you, of course!

206
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,240
I love you!

207
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,799
But still no one's buying.

208
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,120
It's okay.

209
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,919
It's only our first day open.

210
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,399
Want to buy some pork?

211
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:06,480
Come take a look!

212
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,399
Skewers! Get your skewers!

213
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:28,159
Freshly skewered, freshly grilled!

214
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:29,159
Hey, sir!

215
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,039
Come check it out.

216
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:33,120
Smells so good and you're not coming?

217
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,559
You don't know what you're missing.

218
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,240
Here, this one looks good.

219
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,559
Nice one. Let's try it ourselves.

220
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:41,919
Delicious.

221
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:42,679
Is the seasoning okay?

222
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:43,480
Just right.

223
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:43,919
Let me have a taste.

224
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,200
Good, right?

225
00:09:48,279 --> 00:09:49,120
Add a bit more chili.

226
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,720
Insanely tasty.

227
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,440
Boss Hui.

228
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,519
Sister-in-law's selling meat with Yu Tianfang.

229
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,919
She cheated on you. Let me finish her off.

230
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,519
She's not your sister-in-law anymore.

231
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,600
That stupid woman.

232
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,480
So happy with some pork butcher.

233
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,240
Don't rush.

234
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,799
We'll watch from outside first.

235
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,600
In case it's a trap.

236
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:08,080
Move aside, move aside.

237
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,919
Go, go, go.

238
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,360
Yu Tianfang

239
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,360
Chu Feng

240
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,039
Why aren't you selling pork properly?

241
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,159
Now you're grilling skewers?

242
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:28,919
You guys don't get it.

243
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:29,879
Let me tell you something.

244
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,480
This stall's location is bad.

245
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,799
Customers can't see it.

246
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,919
So I have to rely on their noses.

247
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,200
See, once I fire up the charcoal,

248
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,399
the aroma rises,

249
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:39,080
and the hungry crowd follows, right?

250
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,039
This guy is one sly fox.

251
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,720
So this is your big plan to get rich?

252
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,080
Chu Feng,

253
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,879
do you know

254
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,679
what my dream job was as a kid?

255
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,720
To become a cop.

256
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,639
But...

257
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,440
my dad got locked up

258
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,559
a few times for stealing.

259
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,840
I couldn't become a cop.

260
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,600
I could only take odd jobs everywhere,

261
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,639
drifting around,

262
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:01,600
just to put food on the table.

263
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,200
But then later,

264
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,080
I met Boss Bai.

265
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,720
She was the first person

266
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,480
who appreciated my talent.

267
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,120
I really envy you.

268
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:14,919
You get to do what you love.

269
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,759
You don't need to envy me.

270
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,679
As long as you put your heart into it,

271
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:22,039
anything can become your career.

272
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:23,519
Right.

273
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:26,159
From now on, call me the Pork Prince.

274
00:11:28,639 --> 00:11:29,320
What's this?

275
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:31,440
It's nothing.

276
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,840
Stop looking, eat up, the meat's burning.

277
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:33,799
Hey,

278
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,120
I'd like to keep one.

279
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,919
Maybe someone can give us a lead.

280
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,480
Yeah.

281
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,519
Sure.

282
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:39,960
We appreciate it.

283
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,720
Mind if I stick one up here?

284
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,120
Okay.

285
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,679
You guys keep grilling.

286
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,279
Chen Dahui's son has been found.

287
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:54,600
Here, have a skewer.

288
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,639
Do your job well.

289
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,080
Try to get some leads out of him.

290
00:11:59,440 --> 00:11:59,799
Got it.

291
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:02,159
What are you doing?

292
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:03,559
Fox.

293
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,279
Sir,

294
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:04,679
the skewers are ready.

295
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:05,360
I know you.

296
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:05,799
Have a taste.

297
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:06,600
I know you too.

298
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,639
These are grilled skewers.

299
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,200
Have one.

300
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:09,840
Skewers, skewers!

301
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,840
Come, come, come.

302
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,639
Fresh off the grill.

303
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:11,960
Okay.

304
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,039
On the house, on the house.

305
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,399
Here.

306
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:13,960
Money.

307
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,279
Here, take it.

308
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:16,399
I'll be off now.

309
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,600
Tianfang,

310
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,919
congratulations.

311
00:12:22,279 --> 00:12:24,039
Your big plan is officially in business.

312
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:24,679
Open for business!

313
00:12:24,679 --> 00:12:25,320
Two coins.

314
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:26,879
Here, they're done, have some.

315
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:27,519
Eat up.

316
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,679
Let me, here.

317
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,240
Qibao.

318
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:30,399
You eat, I'll serve.

319
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:30,799
Okay.

320
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,279
The smoke's getting to you.

321
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:33,840
It's fine.

